platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Pillow is stuffed with ways to improve your sleep. The app tracks your zs, records your moods, and follows your daily routine to help you establish a consistent sleep pattern, night after night. We love the apps intersection of sleep and data. Tell Pillow about your daily routineincluding your mood, meal times, and amount of caffeine youve consumedand itll begin to learn whats helping and hindering you at night.
Track your sleep, record your moods and meals (and caffeine intake) and follow your daily routine with the app thats stuffed with ways to improve your slumber, night after night.
